    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or dent\u2014it\u2019s been pampered and kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one! It drives like a total dream and still has that new car smell. If you're looking for something that's basically flawless, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 44500.0,
