    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered era, featuring a 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M-Lock limited-slip differential. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and both the rod bearings and VANOS system have been proactively serviced to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis remains rigid, supported by a refreshed suspension with factory-spec bushings and dampers. Finished in concours-level condition, this vehicle offers a pure, analog driving experience with uncompromising mechanical provenance.",
